title: Political Climate - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/3/22
itunes:title: Political Climate - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/3/22
description:
George Noory and Dick Morris discuss whether Donald Trump and Hillary Clinton will run in 2024.  Dick also shares his thoughts on the Biden administration as well as the current state of Iran, Russia and Ukraine.
